import React from 'react'
import Header from './header/header'
import HeroSection from './header/herosection'
import Card from './card/Card'
import Footer from './footer/footer'
function Main() {
  return (
    <>
    <Header/>
    <HeroSection/>
    <Card/>
    <Footer/>
    </>
  )
}

export default Main
